    "Single-leg stance 3.",
    "Crossed leg sway 15 10 min 16 3 days/week",
    "• A hypoallergenic underlay will be placed over the patella as a base.",
    "• Zinc oxide tape will then be applied from the center to the lateral aspect of the patella, inducing medial tilt.",
    "• Subsequently, a medial glide will gather the tissues around the knee."
